---
// PaymentShowroomArrojado.astro
const wppLink = "https://wa.me/5531997289558?text=Ol%C3%A1%2C%20gostaria%20de%20agendar%20uma%20visita%20ao%20showroom%20da%20Cas4!";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white" id="condicoes">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 w-1/2 bg-[#B28D42] -skew-x-12 opacity-90 hidden lg:block -z-10 translate-x-12"></div>
  
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <div class="relative w-full max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-full mt-0 lg:mt-0 order-first lg:order-last">
        
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#B28D42] rounded-2xl translate-x-3 translate-y-3 -z-10 opacity-90 block lg:hidden"></div>
        
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[4/5] bg-slate-100 lg:-translate-x-12">
          <img 
            src="/foto-showroom-cas4.webp" 
            alt="Showroom da Cas4 Pisos e Ambientes em Itabirito" 
            class="object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl text-left bg-[#0A2F5C] lg:bg-transparent p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-0 rounded-2xl lg:rounded-none shadow-xl lg:shadow-none">
        
        <div class="lg:border-l-8 lg:border-[#B28D42] lg:pl-8">
          <h2 class="text-[26px] md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white lg:text-[#0A2F5C] mb-4 md:mb-8 leading-snug">
            Sua obra de alto padrão com condições reais e <span class="text-[#B28D42]">flexíveis</span>.
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-[15px] md:text-lg text-slate-100 lg:text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic border-l-4 border-[#B28D42]/50 pl-4 lg:pl-0 lg:border-none">
            "Acreditamos que a escolha dos acabamentos deve ser a melhor parte da obra. Por isso, simplificamos a parte financeira para você focar no conforto e na estética."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 md:mt-12 flex flex-col gap-6 md:gap-8">
          
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center bg-white/5 lg:bg-transparent p-4 lg:p-0 rounded-xl">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#B28D42] text-[#0A2F5C] font-extrabold mr-4">✓</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-white lg:text-slate-800 text-lg md:text-base">Até 12x sem juros</span>
              <p class="text-slate-200 lg:text-slate-600 text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed hidden sm:block">
                Parcele todos os seus pisos secos e revestimentos no cartão de crédito. Sem surpresas ou taxas ocultas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-row items-center bg-white/5 lg:bg-transparent p-4 lg:p-0 rounded-xl">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#B28D42] text-[#0A2F5C] font-extrabold mr-4">✓</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-white lg:text-slate-800 text-lg md:text-base">Negociação direto com a proprietária</span>
              <p class="text-slate-200 lg:text-slate-600 text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed hidden sm:block">
                Você conversa diretamente com quem tem total autonomia para fechar o melhor negócio para o seu bolso.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-row items-center bg-white/5 lg:bg-transparent p-4 lg:p-0 rounded-xl">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#B28D42] text-[#0A2F5C] font-extrabold mr-4">✓</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-white lg:text-slate-800 text-lg md:text-base">Showroom disponível para visita</span>
              <p class="text-slate-200 lg:text-slate-600 text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed hidden sm:block">
                Sinta a textura dos materiais, veja as cores na luz real e comprove a qualidade antes de decidir.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href={wppLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-full lg:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 text-base font-bold text-[#0A2F5C] lg:text-white transition-all duration-300 bg-[#B28D42] lg:bg-[#0A2F5C] rounded-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1">
            Falar com a equipe no WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>